name: Cralie
description:
This plant lives and transits in the Propane layer of planet Garvanh, for which it's considered a floating plant type. It moves at 5 km per hour and can measure up to 40 meters high and 60 meters wide. Its scent permeats among the diamonds that pass by it and hypnotizes them in such a way that they are trapped around it.

•⋞•⋞•⋞•⋞••••••••••••••••⋟•⋟•⋟•⋟•

At sunset it can be observed levitating among silk rays.
